{"tid":1083633,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有無人覺得2019過咗3個月但已經好多好歌？","createTime":"2019-03-29T18:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T15:12:02.000Z","uid":7326,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac45fa0af289b10f570ffc0d1fa26208224cffc7","tid":1083633,"uid":7326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T18:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b33yVk9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb33yVk9.png&h=e9455f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近開始聽返903，然後留意返好多本地音樂，佢地播得愈多我就聽得愈淘醉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n陳健安首 一吻穿越四十六億歲<br />\n許廷鏗首 偽人<br />\n側田首 懷很久的久<br />\n古巨基首 亂世情侶<br />\n林家謙首 下一位前度<br />\n鄧小巧首 雲吞<br />\n蘇永康首 All that jazz<br />\n<br />\nNowhere Boys首 致旅途中的我！！！<br />\n<br />\n陳凱詠首 想突然（好正，好有Fiona岩岩出道果時既感覺！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有Juno Kay既 其實 寂寞 就如<br />\n同埋張敬軒首 You !! (好想好想remix MJ把聲落去！！)<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多好多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然年年都話香港電影香港樂壇頹，今年感覺係多咗好多衝擊，或者年紀大咗隨性咗對所有野都容易接受咗，但我好撚期待2019年度既頒獎典禮！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f4f171b51122a52a12852906ba583f921032ed","tid":1083633,"uid":52705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T18:13:50.000Z","msg":"kolor初老"},{"pid":"dc5f0ce72f223d247c6a09144a6b1037e266e245","tid":1083633,"uid":7326,"like":0,"dis